data.description: Spacious 1BR+den/office/nursery or formal dining room - the largest 1BR in the complex! This upgraded unit boasts newer appliances and new laminated Pergo flooring in the kitchen, along with a tiled entry and lush, brand new carpet throughout. The original dining room has been transformed into a separate room, offering flexibility as a potential second bedroom. Numerous other upgrades include a new shower door, ceramic tile in the bath, and more!  Conveniently situated on the ground floor, this unit comes with parking underneath and elevator access, ensuring easy mobility with no steps. Enjoy the expansive balcony accessible from sliding doors in both the living room and bedroom.  The complex features excellent recreational facilities, including a spacious heated pool, relaxing spa, saunas, a well-equipped gym, and a fantastic clubhouse. Surrounded by open space, trees, and various activities, this residence provides a comfortable and enjoyable living experience. The beach is 3 minutes away. Don't miss the opportunity to make this upgraded and spacious unit your new home!
